Fog collection may be a suitable method for water collection in arid regions that experience fog and dew. 

It is not a simple process however, and a Chilean project (described in the [[Wikipedia:Fog collection|Wikipedia article]]) did not give the desired results.

==Organizations==
* [[FogQuest]],[http://www.fogquest.org] an international, non-governmental, non-profit organization, which implements and promotes the "environmentally appropriate, socially beneficial and economically viable use of fog, [[rain]] and dew as sustainable water resources for people in arid regions of developing countries."


